## MarkerTechniqueParams.iconReserveSpace property

If `false`<!-- -->, icon will not reserve screen space, other markers will be able to overlap. If not defined, the property value from `iconReserveSpace` will be used.  `true`

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
iconReserveSpace?: boolean;
```
